  <brief_title>Intraperitoneal Techniques of Local Anaesthesia During Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of Intraperitoneal Local Anaesthetic Techniques During Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy: A Double Blind Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
